T1  - FOREIGN DIRECT INVESTMENT IN A TWO-TIER OLIGOPOLY: COORDINATION, VERTICAL INTEGRATION, AND WELFARE*
AU  - Lin, Ping
AU  - Saggi, Kamal
Y1  - 2011/11/01
PY  - 2011
DA  - 2011/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-2354.2011.00667.x
T2  - International Economic Review
